➜新田：油茶丰收采摘忙
http://www.sohu.com/a/427314042_100180399	7967
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201026/07d84029163242c497ddc325dfb22264.png" /></p>
